prompts.frontCover:
A flat 2D botanical illustration style greeting card front. In the center, there is a cartoon illustration of a happy couple, Lao Lao and Jordan, who highly resemble the people in the reference photo.

Lao Lao, on the left, is an East Asian woman with long, straight dark brown hair. She is smiling, wearing thin gold-rimmed glasses, a light blue crewneck sweatshirt (with no logos or text), and black pants. Her arms are crossed in front of her.

Jordan, on the right, is a young man of Southeast Asian descent with short, textured dark hair. He is standing slightly behind Lao Lao, hugging her from behind with his arms wrapped around her waist. He has a big, warm smile and is wearing a tan/brown hoodie (with no logos or text) and dark reddish-brown pants.

They are playfully struggling over a giant, comically oversized birthday cupcake with bright pink frosting and a single lit candle on top, holding it between them. Lao Lao is trying to pull it towards herself with a mischievous grin, while Jordan is playfully trying to pull it back, laughing.

The couple is framed by an elegant, asymmetrical wreath of detailed botanical elements. This includes lush monstera leaves, delicate fern fronds, eucalyptus branches, and vibrant, blooming pink peonies and white anemones, all rendered in soft, organic watercolor textures.

In the center of the card, slightly overlapping the botanical wreath at the top, is the text "Happy Birthday to my favorite human bean" in a beautiful, readable, and elegant handwritten cursive script. The text is colored a deep charcoal gray. The background is a solid, soft cream color.

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
